"Définit les pages liées à l’inscription grossiste, la connexion et les "
"conditions du programme de vente en gros."

#: includes/class-wwlc-settings.php:444
msgid "Wholesale Login"
msgstr "Connexion grossiste"

#: includes/class-wwlc-settings.php:446
msgid ""
"This is the page where your wholesale customers login to their accounts."
msgstr "C'est la page où les clients grossistes se connectent à leurs comptes."

#: includes/class-wwlc-settings.php:455
msgid "Wholesale Registration"
msgstr "Inscription grossiste"

#: includes/class-wwlc-settings.php:457
msgid "This is the page where new leads can register for a wholesale account."
msgstr ""
"C'est la page où les nouveaux clients peuvent s’incrire pour un compte "
"grosssite."

#: includes/class-wwlc-settings.php:467
msgid "Allow logged-in admin and shop managers to view registration page"
msgstr ""
"Autoriser l'administrateur connecté et les responsables de boutique à "
"afficher la page d'inscription"

#: includes/class-wwlc-settings.php:472
msgid "Wholesale Registration Thank You"
msgstr "Remerciement d’inscription grossiste"

#: includes/class-wwlc-settings.php:474
msgid ""
"This is where customers are redirected immediately after registering for "
"their wholesale account."
msgstr ""
"C'est là que vos clients seront redirigés immédiatement après inscription de "
"leur compte grossiste."

#: includes/class-wwlc-settings.php:483
msgid "Login Redirect"
msgstr "Redirection de connexion"

#: includes/class-wwlc-settings.php:485
msgid ""
"This is where wholesale customers are redirected immediately after logging "
"in."
msgstr ""
"C'est là que les clients grossistes sont redirigés immédiatement après leur "
"connexion."

#: includes/class-wwlc-settings.php:494
msgid "Logout Redirect"
msgstr "Redirection à la déconnexion"

#: includes/class-wwlc-settings.php:496
msgid ""
"This is where wholesale customers are redirected immediately after logging "
"out."
msgstr ""
"C'est là que les clients grossistes sont redirigés immédiatement après leur "
"déconnexion."

#: includes/class-wwlc-settings.php:505 includes/class-wwlc-settings.php:1383
#: includes/class-wwlc-settings.php:1737
msgid "Terms & Conditions"
msgstr "Conditions Générales de Vente"

#: includes/class-wwlc-settings.php:507
msgid ""
"If you are showing terms & conditions on your registration form, this is "
"where they will link to."
msgstr ""
"Si vous montrez les Conditions Générales de Ventes dans le formulaire "
"d'inscription, c'est vers cela que le lien pointera."

#: includes/class-wwlc-settings.php:521
msgid "Lead Actions"
msgstr "Actions de référencement"

#: includes/class-wwlc-settings.php:523
msgid ""
"These settings describe what happens to when processing a new wholesale lead."
msgstr ""
"Ces paramètres décrivent ce qui se produit quand on procède à un nouveau "
"référencement de client grossiste."

#: includes/class-wwlc-settings.php:528
msgid "New Lead Role"
msgstr "Nouveau rôle du référencé"

#: includes/class-wwlc-settings.php:530
msgid ""
"This is the user role that your wholesale customers will receive once they "
"have been approved."
msgstr ""
"C'est le rôle utilisateur que vos clients grossistes recevront une fois "
"qu'ils auront été approuvés."

#: includes/class-wwlc-settings.php:535
msgid "Select Some User Roles..."
msgstr "Sélectionnez des rôles utilisateurs…"

#: includes/class-wwlc-settings.php:541
msgid "Auto Approve New Leads"
msgstr "Auto-approuvez les nouveaux référencements"

#: includes/class-wwlc-settings.php:545
msgid ""
"Note: When it's set to Automatic Approval, users will be automatically "
"logged-in after successful registration."
msgstr ""
"Note: Quand l’approbation automatique est active, les utilisateurs seront "
"automatiquement connectés après une inscription réussie. "

#: includes/class-wwlc-settings.php:547
msgid ""
"Manual Approval Required – new registrations are held in a moderation queue "
"and require an administrator or store manager to approve them."
msgstr ""
"Approbation manuelle requise - les nouvelles inscriptions sont conservées "
"dans une file de modération et nécessitent qu’un administrateur ou "
"gestionnaire de boutique les approuve."

#: includes/class-wwlc-settings.php:548
msgid ""
"Automatic Approval – new registrations are automatically approved after "
"submitting the wholesale registration form."
msgstr ""
"Approbation automatique - les nouvelles inscriptions seront automatiquement "
"approuvées après soumission du formulaire d’inscription grossiste."

#: includes/class-wwlc-settings.php:553
msgid "Account Upgrade"
msgstr "Mettre à jour le compte"

#: includes/class-wwlc-settings.php:555
msgid ""
"Allow existing customers to request an account upgrade. Existing customers "
"must fill-up and submit the lead capture registration form to request an "
"upgrade. Note: once approved, the role will be based on the New Lead Role "
"set above."
msgstr ""
"Permet aux clients existants de demander une mise à jour de leur compte. Les "
"clients existants doivent remplir et soumettre le formulaire de "
"référencement pour leur demande de mise à jour. Note: une fois approuvée, "
"leur rôle sera fondée sur le Nouveau rôle du référencé défini ci-dessus."

#: includes/class-wwlc-settings.php:560
msgid "Show Account Upgrade Message"
msgstr "Afficher le message de mise à jour"

#: includes/class-wwlc-settings.php:562
msgid ""
"Display account upgrade message and link to upgrade account registration "
"form in \"My account\" page for standard customers."
msgstr ""
